ANXIETY=~ STAI_Par1 + STAI_Par2 + STAI_Par3
OPEN=~ Open_Par1 + Open_Par2 + Open_Par3
LEAD=~ Lead_Par1 + Lead_Par2 + Lead_Par3

##Structural relationships

ANXIETY~a*ATTACH
OPEN~c*ATTACH
LEAD~b*ANXIETY + d*OPEN

##indirect effect anxiety path
